These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, sprite, tea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, weightlifting, baseball, soccer
City: edinburgh, london, rome, hamburg, prague
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts, romance, zombie, superhero
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
10. the person traveling to rome is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
13. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
14. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
15. the person traveling to hamburg is the person drinking sprite##1
16. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | hot-chocolate   | sprite     | tea      | milk      |
| Sport           | weightlifting | soccer | cricket    | baseball | climbing |
| City   | rome       | edinburgh         | hamburg      | london      | prague    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | zombie         | martial-arts | superhero  | scientific   |

