There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, american, egyptian, dutch
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left of the dutch##1
 6. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the japanese##2
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
11. the egyptian is on the right of the japanese##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
13. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the american##3
14. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
