 3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 9. the person who likes grey is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who likes red##2
13. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
14. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
