13. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's birthday is in august##1
15. the person drinking sprite is the person watching satire movies##1
16. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
