 8. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes light-blue and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 9. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is the fonseca-smoker##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
13. the person who likes ebony is the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
