16. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |       3       |     4     |       5       |
| Job          | electrician  | paramedic        | engineer       | pilot | videographer    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | hiking        | dancing       | cooking   | fanta-climbing |
| Beverage   | water         | sprite        | fanta          | hot-chocolate     | lemonade    |
| Color         | lavender       | light-blue | chestnut | grey   | white      |

